cmiFaRegTotalVisitors.name: cmiFaRegTotalVisitors
cmiFaRegTotalVisitors.reference: RFC-2006 - Mobile IP MIB Definition using SMIv2
cmiFaRegTotalVisitors.description: The current number of entries in faVisitorTable. faVisitorTable contains the foreign agent's visitor list. The foreign agent updates this table in response to registration events from mobile nodes.

cmiFaRegVisitorTable.name: cmiFaRegVisitorTable
cmiFaRegVisitorTable.description: A table containing the foreign agent's visitor list. The foreign agent updates this table in response to registration events from mobile nodes. This table provides the same information as faVisitorTable of MIP-MIB. The difference is that indices of the table are changed so that visitors which are not identified by the IP address will also be included in the table.

cmiFaRegVisitorEntry.name: cmiFaRegVisitorEntry
cmiFaRegVisitorEntry.description: Information for one visitor regarding registration.

cmiFaRegVisitorIdentifierType.name: cmiFaRegVisitorIdentifierType
cmiFaRegVisitorIdentifierType.description: The type of the visitor's identifier.

cmiFaRegVisitorIdentifier.name: cmiFaRegVisitorIdentifier
cmiFaRegVisitorIdentifier.description: The identifier associated with the visitor.

cmiFaRegVisitorHomeAddress.name: cmiFaRegVisitorHomeAddress
cmiFaRegVisitorHomeAddress.description: Home (IP) address of visiting mobile node.

cmiFaRegVisitorHomeAgentAddress.name: cmiFaRegVisitorHomeAgentAddress
cmiFaRegVisitorHomeAgentAddress.description: Home agent IP address for that visiting mobile node.

cmiFaRegVisitorTimeGranted.name: cmiFaRegVisitorTimeGranted
cmiFaRegVisitorTimeGranted.description: The lifetime granted to the mobile node for this registration. Only valid if faVisitorRegIsAccepted is true(1).

cmiFaRegVisitorTimeRemaining.name: cmiFaRegVisitorTimeRemaining
cmiFaRegVisitorTimeRemaining.description: The time remaining until the registration is expired. It has the same initial value as cmiFaRegVisitorTimeGranted, and is counted down by the foreign agent.

cmiFaRegVisitorRegFlags.name: cmiFaRegVisitorRegFlags
cmiFaRegVisitorRegFlags.description: Registration flags sent by the mobile node.

cmiFaRegVisitorRegIDLow.name: cmiFaRegVisitorRegIDLow
cmiFaRegVisitorRegIDLow.description: Low 32 bits of Identification used in that registration by the mobile node.

cmiFaRegVisitorRegIDHigh.name: cmiFaRegVisitorRegIDHigh
cmiFaRegVisitorRegIDHigh.description: High 32 bits of Identification used in that registration by the mobile node.

cmiFaRegVisitorRegIsAccepted.name: cmiFaRegVisitorRegIsAccepted
cmiFaRegVisitorRegIsAccepted.description: Whether the registration has been accepted or not. If it is false(2), this registration is still pending for reply.

cmiFaInitRegRequestsReceived.name: cmiFaInitRegRequestsReceived
cmiFaInitRegRequestsReceived.description: Total number of initial Registration Requests received by the foreign agent.

cmiFaInitRegRequestsRelayed.name: cmiFaInitRegRequestsRelayed
cmiFaInitRegRequestsRelayed.description: Total number of initial Registration Requests relayed by the foreign agent to the home agent.

cmiFaInitRegRequestsDenied.name: cmiFaInitRegRequestsDenied
cmiFaInitRegRequestsDenied.description: Total number of initial Registration Requests denied by the foreign agent. The reasons for which FA denies a request include: 1. FA CHAP authentication failures. 2. HA is not reachable. 3. No HA address set in the packet.

cmiFaInitRegRequestsDiscarded.name: cmiFaInitRegRequestsDiscarded
cmiFaInitRegRequestsDiscarded.description: Total number of initial Registration Requests discarded by the foreign agent. The reasons for which FA discards a request include: 1. ip mobile foreign-service is not enabled on the interface on which the request is received. 2. NAI length exceeds the length of the packet. 3. There are no active COAs.

cmiFaInitRegRepliesValidFromHA.name: cmiFaInitRegRepliesValidFromHA
cmiFaInitRegRepliesValidFromHA.description: Total number of initial valid Registration Replies from the home agent to foreign agent.

cmiFaInitRegRepliesValidRelayMN.name: cmiFaInitRegRepliesValidRelayMN
cmiFaInitRegRepliesValidRelayMN.description: Total number of initial Registration Replies relayed to MN by the foreign agent.

cmiFaReRegRequestsReceived.name: cmiFaReRegRequestsReceived
cmiFaReRegRequestsReceived.description: Total number of Re-Registration Requests received by the foreign agent from mobile nodes.

cmiFaReRegRequestsRelayed.name: cmiFaReRegRequestsRelayed
cmiFaReRegRequestsRelayed.description: Total number of Re-Registration Requests relayed to MN by the foreign agent.

cmiFaReRegRequestsDenied.name: cmiFaReRegRequestsDenied
cmiFaReRegRequestsDenied.description: Total number of Re-Registration Requests denied by the foreign agent. Refer cmiFaInitRegRequestsDenied for the reasons for which FA denies a request.

cmiFaReRegRequestsDiscarded.name: cmiFaReRegRequestsDiscarded
cmiFaReRegRequestsDiscarded.description: Total number of Re-Registration Requests discarded by the foreign agent. Refer cmiFaInitRegRequestsDiscarded for the reasons for which FA discards a request.

cmiFaReRegRepliesValidFromHA.name: cmiFaReRegRepliesValidFromHA
cmiFaReRegRepliesValidFromHA.description: Total number of valid Re-Registration Replies from home agent.

cmiFaReRegRepliesValidRelayToMN.name: cmiFaReRegRepliesValidRelayToMN
cmiFaReRegRepliesValidRelayToMN.description: Total number of valid Re-Registration Replies relayed to MN by the foreign agent.

cmiFaDeRegRequestsReceived.name: cmiFaDeRegRequestsReceived
cmiFaDeRegRequestsReceived.description: Total number of De-Registration Requests received by the foreign agent.

cmiFaDeRegRequestsRelayed.name: cmiFaDeRegRequestsRelayed
cmiFaDeRegRequestsRelayed.description: Total number of De-Registration Requests relayed to home agent by the foreign agent.

cmiFaDeRegRequestsDenied.name: cmiFaDeRegRequestsDenied
cmiFaDeRegRequestsDenied.description: Total number of De-Registration Requests denied by the foreign agent. Refer cmiFaInitRegRequestsDenied for the reasons for which FA denies a request.

cmiFaDeRegRequestsDiscarded.name: cmiFaDeRegRequestsDiscarded
cmiFaDeRegRequestsDiscarded.description: Total number of De-Registration Requests discarded by the foreign agent. Refer cmiFaInitRegRequestsDiscarded for the reasons for which FA discards a request.

cmiFaDeRegRepliesValidFromHA.name: cmiFaDeRegRepliesValidFromHA
cmiFaDeRegRepliesValidFromHA.description: Total number of valid De-Registration Replies received from the home agent by the foreign agent.

cmiFaDeRegRepliesValidRelayToMN.name: cmiFaDeRegRepliesValidRelayToMN
cmiFaDeRegRepliesValidRelayToMN.description: Total number of De-Registration Replies relayed to the MN by the foreign agent.

cmiHaRegTotalMobilityBindings.name: cmiHaRegTotalMobilityBindings
cmiHaRegTotalMobilityBindings.reference: RFC-2006 - Mobile IP MIB Definition using SMIv2
cmiHaRegTotalMobilityBindings.description: The current number of entries in haMobilityBindingTable. haMobilityBindingTable contains the home agent's mobility binding list. The home agent updates this table in response to registration events from mobile nodes.

cmiHaRegMobilityBindingTable.name: cmiHaRegMobilityBindingTable
cmiHaRegMobilityBindingTable.description: The home agent updates this table in response to registration events from mobile nodes.

cmiHaRegMobilityBindingEntry.name: cmiHaRegMobilityBindingEntry
cmiHaRegMobilityBindingEntry.description: Additional information about a particular entry on the mobility binding list beyond that provided by MIP MIB haMobilityBindingEntry.

cmiHaRegMnIdentifierType.name: cmiHaRegMnIdentifierType
cmiHaRegMnIdentifierType.description: The type of the mobile node's identifier.

cmiHaRegMnIdentifier.name: cmiHaRegMnIdentifier
cmiHaRegMnIdentifier.description: The identifier associated with the mobile node.

cmiHaRegCounterTable.name: cmiHaRegCounterTable
cmiHaRegCounterTable.description: A table containing registration statistics for all mobile nodes authorized to use this home agent. This table provides the same information as haCounterTable of MIP MIB. The only difference is that indices of table are changed so that mobile nodes which are not identified by the IP address will also be included in the table.

cmiHaRegCounterEntry.name: cmiHaRegCounterEntry
cmiHaRegCounterEntry.description: Registration statistics for a single mobile node.

cmiHaRegMnIdType.name: cmiHaRegMnIdType
cmiHaRegMnIdType.description: The type of the mobile node's identifier.

cmiHaRegMnId.name: cmiHaRegMnId
cmiHaRegMnId.description: The identifier associated with the mobile node.

cmiHaRegServAcceptedRequests.name: cmiHaRegServAcceptedRequests
cmiHaRegServAcceptedRequests.description: Total number of service requests for the mobile node accepted by the home agent (Code 0 + Code 1).

cmiHaRegServDeniedRequests.name: cmiHaRegServDeniedRequests
cmiHaRegServDeniedRequests.description: Total number of service requests for the mobile node denied by the home agent (sum of all registrations denied with Code 128 through Code 159).

cmiHaRegOverallServTime.name: cmiHaRegOverallServTime
cmiHaRegOverallServTime.description: Overall service time that has accumulated for the mobile node since the home agent last rebooted.

cmiHaRegRecentServAcceptedTime.name: cmiHaRegRecentServAcceptedTime
cmiHaRegRecentServAcceptedTime.description: The time at which the most recent Registration Request was accepted by the home agent for this mobile node.

cmiHaRegRecentServDeniedTime.name: cmiHaRegRecentServDeniedTime
cmiHaRegRecentServDeniedTime.description: The time at which the most recent Registration Request was denied by the home agent for this mobile node.

cmiHaRegRecentServDeniedCode.name: cmiHaRegRecentServDeniedCode
cmiHaRegRecentServDeniedCode.description: The Code indicating the reason why the most recent Registration Request for this mobile node was rejected by the home agent.

cmiHaRegTotalProcLocRegs.name: cmiHaRegTotalProcLocRegs
cmiHaRegTotalProcLocRegs.description: The total number of Registration Requests processed by the home agent. It includes only those Registration Requests which were authenticated locally by the home agent.

cmiHaRegMaxProcLocInMinRegs.name: cmiHaRegMaxProcLocInMinRegs
cmiHaRegMaxProcLocInMinRegs.description: The maximum number of Registration Requests processed in a minute by the home agent. It includes only those Registration Requests which were authenticated locally by the home agent.

cmiHaRegDateMaxRegsProcLoc.name: cmiHaRegDateMaxRegsProcLoc
cmiHaRegDateMaxRegsProcLoc.description: The time at which number of Registration Requests processed in a minute by the home agent were maximum. It includes only those Registration Requests which were authenticated locally by the home agent.

cmiHaRegProcLocInLastMinRegs.name: cmiHaRegProcLocInLastMinRegs
cmiHaRegProcLocInLastMinRegs.description: The number of Registration Requests processed in the last minute by the home agent. It includes only those Registration Requests which were authenticated locally by the home agent.

cmiHaRegTotalProcByAAARegs.name: cmiHaRegTotalProcByAAARegs
cmiHaRegTotalProcByAAARegs.description: The total number of Registration Requests processed by the home agent. It includes only those Registration Requests which were authenticated by the AAA server.

cmiHaRegMaxProcByAAAInMinRegs.name: cmiHaRegMaxProcByAAAInMinRegs
cmiHaRegMaxProcByAAAInMinRegs.description: The maximum number of Registration Requests processed in a minute by the home agent. It includes only those Registration Requests which were authenticated by the AAA server.

cmiHaRegDateMaxRegsProcByAAA.name: cmiHaRegDateMaxRegsProcByAAA
cmiHaRegDateMaxRegsProcByAAA.description: The time at which number of Registration Requests processed in a minute by the home agent were maximum. It includes only those Registration Requests which were authenticated by the AAA server.

cmiHaRegProcAAAInLastByMinRegs.name: cmiHaRegProcAAAInLastByMinRegs
cmiHaRegProcAAAInLastByMinRegs.description: The number of Registration Requests processed in the last minute by the home agent. It includes only those Registration Requests which were authenticated by the AAA server.

cmiHaRegAvgTimeRegsProcByAAA.name: cmiHaRegAvgTimeRegsProcByAAA
cmiHaRegAvgTimeRegsProcByAAA.description: The average time taken by the home agent to process a Registration Request. It is calculated based on only those Registration Requests which were authenticated by the AAA server.

cmiHaRegMaxTimeRegsProcByAAA.name: cmiHaRegMaxTimeRegsProcByAAA
cmiHaRegMaxTimeRegsProcByAAA.description: The maximum time taken by the home agent to process a Registration Request. It considers only those Registration Requests which were authenticated by the AAA server.

cmiHaRegRequestsReceived.name: cmiHaRegRequestsReceived
cmiHaRegRequestsReceived.description: Total number of Registration Requests received by the home agent. This include initial registration requests, re-registration requests and de-registration requests.

cmiHaRegRequestsDenied.name: cmiHaRegRequestsDenied
cmiHaRegRequestsDenied.description: Total number of Registration Requests denied by the home agent. The reasons for which HA denies a request include: 1. Can't allocate IP address for MN. 2. Request parsing failed. 3. NAI length exceeds the packet length.

cmiHaRegRequestsDiscarded.name: cmiHaRegRequestsDiscarded
cmiHaRegRequestsDiscarded.description: Total number of Registration Requests discarded by the home agent. The reasons for which HA discards a request include: 1. ip mobile home-agent service is not enabled. 2. HA-CHAP authentication failed. 3. MN Security Association retrieval failed.

cmiHaEncapUnavailable.name: cmiHaEncapUnavailable
cmiHaEncapUnavailable.description: Total number of Registration Requests denied by the home agent due to an unsupported encapsulation.

cmiHaNAICheckFailures.name: cmiHaNAICheckFailures
cmiHaNAICheckFailures.description: Total number of Registration Requests denied by the home agent due to an NAI check failures.

cmiHaInitRegRequestsReceived.name: cmiHaInitRegRequestsReceived
cmiHaInitRegRequestsReceived.description: Total number of initial Registration Requests received by the home agent.

cmiHaInitRegRequestsAccepted.name: cmiHaInitRegRequestsAccepted
cmiHaInitRegRequestsAccepted.description: Total number of initial Registration Requests accepted by the home agent.

cmiHaInitRegRequestsDenied.name: cmiHaInitRegRequestsDenied
cmiHaInitRegRequestsDenied.description: Total number of initial Registration Requests denied by the home agent. Refer cmiHaRegRequestsReceived for the reasons for which HA denies a request.

cmiHaInitRegRequestsDiscarded.name: cmiHaInitRegRequestsDiscarded
cmiHaInitRegRequestsDiscarded.description: Total number of initial Registration Requests discarded by the home agent. Refer cmiHaRegRequestsDiscarded for the reasons for which HA discards a request.

cmiHaReRegRequestsReceived.name: cmiHaReRegRequestsReceived
cmiHaReRegRequestsReceived.description: Total number of Re-Registration Requests received by the home agent.

cmiHaReRegRequestsAccepted.name: cmiHaReRegRequestsAccepted
cmiHaReRegRequestsAccepted.description: Total number of Re-Registration Requests accepted by the home agent.

cmiHaReRegRequestsDenied.name: cmiHaReRegRequestsDenied
cmiHaReRegRequestsDenied.description: Total number of Re-Registration Requests denied by the home agent. Refer cmiHaRegRequestsReceived for the reasons for which HA denies a request.

cmiHaReRegRequestsDiscarded.name: cmiHaReRegRequestsDiscarded
cmiHaReRegRequestsDiscarded.description: Total number of Re-Registration Requests discarded by the home agent. Refer cmiHaRegRequestsDiscarded for the reasons for which HA discards a request.

cmiHaDeRegRequestsReceived.name: cmiHaDeRegRequestsReceived
cmiHaDeRegRequestsReceived.description: Total number of De-Registration Requests received by the home agent.

cmiHaDeRegRequestsAccepted.name: cmiHaDeRegRequestsAccepted
cmiHaDeRegRequestsAccepted.description: Total number of De-Registration Requests accepted by the home agent.

cmiHaDeRegRequestsDenied.name: cmiHaDeRegRequestsDenied
cmiHaDeRegRequestsDenied.description: Total number of De-Registration Requests denied by the home agent. Refer cmiHaRegRequestsReceived for the reasons for which HA denies a request.

cmiHaDeRegRequestsDiscarded.name: cmiHaDeRegRequestsDiscarded
cmiHaDeRegRequestsDiscarded.description: Total number of De-Registration Requests discarded by the home agent. Refer cmiHaRegRequestsDiscarded for the reasons for which HA discards a request.

cmiHaRedunSentBUs.name: cmiHaRedunSentBUs
cmiHaRedunSentBUs.description: Total number of binding updates sent by the home agent.

cmiHaRedunFailedBUs.name: cmiHaRedunFailedBUs
cmiHaRedunFailedBUs.description: Total number of binding updates sent by the home agent for which no acknowledgement is received from the standby home agent.

cmiHaRedunReceivedBUAcks.name: cmiHaRedunReceivedBUAcks
cmiHaRedunReceivedBUAcks.description: Total number of acknowledgements received in response to binding updates sent by the home agent.

cmiHaRedunTotalSentBUs.name: cmiHaRedunTotalSentBUs
cmiHaRedunTotalSentBUs.description: Total number of binding updates sent by the home agent including retransmissions of same binding update.

cmiHaRedunReceivedBUs.name: cmiHaRedunReceivedBUs
cmiHaRedunReceivedBUs.description: Total number of binding updates received by the home agent.

cmiHaRedunSentBUAcks.name: cmiHaRedunSentBUAcks
cmiHaRedunSentBUAcks.description: Total number of acknowledgements sent in response to binding updates received by the home agent.

cmiHaRedunSentBIReqs.name: cmiHaRedunSentBIReqs
cmiHaRedunSentBIReqs.description: Total number of binding information requests sent by the home agent.

cmiHaRedunFailedBIReqs.name: cmiHaRedunFailedBIReqs
cmiHaRedunFailedBIReqs.description: Total number of binding information requests sent by the home agent for which no reply is received from the active home agent.

cmiHaRedunTotalSentBIReqs.name: cmiHaRedunTotalSentBIReqs
cmiHaRedunTotalSentBIReqs.description: Total number of binding information requests sent by the home agent including retransmissions of the same request.

cmiHaRedunReceivedBIReps.name: cmiHaRedunReceivedBIReps
cmiHaRedunReceivedBIReps.description: Total number of binding information replies received by the home agent.

cmiHaRedunDroppedBIReps.name: cmiHaRedunDroppedBIReps
cmiHaRedunDroppedBIReps.description: Total number of binding information replies dropped since there is no corresponding binding information request sent by the home agent.

cmiHaRedunSentBIAcks.name: cmiHaRedunSentBIAcks
cmiHaRedunSentBIAcks.description: Total number of acknowledgements sent in response to binding information replies received by the home agent.

cmiHaRedunReceivedBIReqs.name: cmiHaRedunReceivedBIReqs
cmiHaRedunReceivedBIReqs.description: Total number of binding information requests received by the home agent.

cmiHaRedunSentBIReps.name: cmiHaRedunSentBIReps
cmiHaRedunSentBIReps.description: Total number of binding information replies sent by the home agent.

cmiHaRedunFailedBIReps.name: cmiHaRedunFailedBIReps
cmiHaRedunFailedBIReps.description: Total number of binding information replies sent by by the home agent for which no acknowledgement is received from the standby home agent.

cmiHaRedunTotalSentBIReps.name: cmiHaRedunTotalSentBIReps
cmiHaRedunTotalSentBIReps.description: Total number of binding information replies sent by the home agent including retransmissions of the same reply.

cmiHaRedunReceivedBIAcks.name: cmiHaRedunReceivedBIAcks
cmiHaRedunReceivedBIAcks.description: Total number of acknowledgements received in response to binding information replies sent by the home agent.

cmiHaRedunDroppedBIAcks.name: cmiHaRedunDroppedBIAcks
cmiHaRedunDroppedBIAcks.description: Total number of acknowledgements dropped by the home agent since there are no corresponding binding information replies sent by it.

cmiHaRedunSecViolations.name: cmiHaRedunSecViolations
cmiHaRedunSecViolations.description: Total number of security violations in the home agent caused by processing of the packets received from the peer home agent. Security violations can occur due to the following reasons. - the authenticator value in the packet is invalid. - value stored in the identification field of the packet is invalid.

cmiSecAssocsCount.name: cmiSecAssocsCount
cmiSecAssocsCount.description: Total number of mobility security associations known to the entity i.e. the number of entries in the cmiSecAssocTable.

cmiSecAssocTable.name: cmiSecAssocTable
cmiSecAssocTable.description: A table containing Mobility Security Associations. This table provides the same information as mipSecAssocTable of MIP MIB. The differences are: - indices of the table are changed so that mobile nodes which are not identified by the IP address will also be included in the table. - rowStatus object is added to the table.

cmiSecPeerIdentifierType.name: cmiSecPeerIdentifierType
cmiSecPeerIdentifierType.description: The type of the peer entity's identifier.

cmiSecPeerIdentifier.name: cmiSecPeerIdentifier
cmiSecPeerIdentifier.description: The identifier of the peer entity with which this node shares the mobility security association.

cmiSecSPI.name: cmiSecSPI
cmiSecSPI.description: The SPI is the 4-byte index within the Mobility Security Association which selects the specific security parameters to be used to authenticate the peer, i.e. the rest of the variables in this cmiSecAssocEntry.

cmiSecAlgorithmType.name: cmiSecAlgorithmType
cmiSecAlgorithmType.description: Type of authentication algorithm. other(1) Any other authentication algorithm not specified here. md5(2) MD5 message-digest algorithm.

cmiSecAlgorithmMode.name: cmiSecAlgorithmMode
cmiSecAlgorithmMode.description: Security mode used by this algorithm. other(1) Any other mode not specified here. prefixSuffix(2) In this mode, data over which authenticator value needs to be calculated is preceded and followed by the 128 bit shared secret key.

cmiSecKey.name: cmiSecKey
cmiSecKey.description: The shared secret key for the security associations. Reading this object will always return zero length value.

cmiSecReplayMethod.name: cmiSecReplayMethod
cmiSecReplayMethod.description: The replay-protection method supported for this SPI within this Mobility Security Association. other(1) Any other replay protection method not specified here. timestamps(2) Timestamp based replay protection method. nonces(3) Nonce based replay protection method.

cmiSecStatus.name: cmiSecStatus
cmiSecStatus.description: The row status for this table.

cmiSecViolationTable.name: cmiSecViolationTable
cmiSecViolationTable.reference: RFC-2002 - IP Mobility Support, sections 3.6.2.1, 3.7.2.1 and 3.8.2.1
cmiSecViolationTable.description: A table containing information about security violations. This table provides the same information as mipSecViolationTable of MIP MIB. The only difference is that indices of the table are changed so that mobile nodes which are not identified by the IP address will also be included in the table.

cmiSecViolationEntry.name: cmiSecViolationEntry
cmiSecViolationEntry.description: Information about one particular security violation.

cmiSecViolatorIdentifier.name: cmiSecViolatorIdentifier
cmiSecViolatorIdentifier.description: Violator's identifier. The violator is not necessary in the cmiSecAssocTable.

cmiSecTotalViolations.name: cmiSecTotalViolations
cmiSecTotalViolations.description: Total number of security violations for this peer.

cmiSecRecentViolationSPI.name: cmiSecRecentViolationSPI
cmiSecRecentViolationSPI.description: SPI of the most recent security violation for this peer. If the security violation is due to an identification mismatch, then this is the SPI from the Mobile-Home Authentication Extension. If the security violation is due to an invalid authenticator, then this is the SPI from the offending authentication extension. In all other cases, it should be set to zero.

cmiSecRecentViolationTime.name: cmiSecRecentViolationTime
cmiSecRecentViolationTime.description: Time of the most recent security violation for this peer.

cmiSecRecentViolationIDLow.name: cmiSecRecentViolationIDLow
cmiSecRecentViolationIDLow.description: Low-order 32 bits of identification used in request or reply of the most recent security violation for this peer.

cmiSecRecentViolationIDHigh.name: cmiSecRecentViolationIDHigh
cmiSecRecentViolationIDHigh.description: High-order 32 bits of identification used in request or reply of the most recent security violation for this peer.

cmiSecRecentViolationReason.name: cmiSecRecentViolationReason
cmiSecRecentViolationReason.description: Reason for the most recent security violation for this peer.

cmiMaRegMaxInMinuteRegs.name: cmiMaRegMaxInMinuteRegs
cmiMaRegMaxInMinuteRegs.description: The maximum number of Registration Requests received in a minute by the mobility agent.

cmiMaRegDateMaxRegsReceived.name: cmiMaRegDateMaxRegsReceived
cmiMaRegDateMaxRegsReceived.description: The time at which number of Registration Requests received in a minute by the mobility agent were maximum.

cmiMaRegInLastMinuteRegs.name: cmiMaRegInLastMinuteRegs
cmiMaRegInLastMinuteRegs.description: The number of Registration Requests received in the last minute by the mobility agent.
